msgstr "La capa vectorial poligonal saliente"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2383
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``qgis:eliminateselectedpolygons``"
msgstr "**Algoritmo ID**: ``qgis:eliminateselectedpolygons``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2393
msgid "Explode lines"
msgstr "Explotar lineas"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2394
msgid ""
"Takes a lines layer and creates a new one in which each line layer is "
"replaced by a set of lines representing the segments in the original line."
msgstr ""
"Toma una capa de líneas y crea una nueva en la que cada capa de línea se "
"reemplaza por un conjunto de líneas que representan los segmentos en la "
"línea original."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2398
msgid ""
"Each line in the resulting layer contains only a start and an end point, "
"with no intermediate vertices between them."
msgstr ""
"Cada línea en la capa resultante contiene solo un punto inicial y final, sin"
" vértices intermedios entre ellos."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2401
msgid ""
"If the input layer consists of CircularStrings or CompoundCurves, the output"
" layer will be of the same type and contain only single curve segments."
msgstr ""
"Si la capa de entrada está formada por CircularStrings o CompoundCurves, la "
"capa de salida será del mismo tipo y solo contendrá segmentos de curva "
"únicos."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2407
msgid "This algorithm does not require valid geometries as input."
msgstr "Este algoritmo no requiere geometrías válidas como entrada."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2412
msgid "The original line layer and the exploded one"
msgstr "La capa de lineas original y la explotada"

