#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5665
msgid "Roundness"
msgstr "Redondez"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5667
msgid ""
"Calculates the roundness of each feature and stores it as a new field "
"``roundness``. The input vector layer must contain polygons."
msgstr ""
"Calcula la redondez de cada característica y la almacena como un nuevo campo"
" denominado ``roundness``. La capa vectorial de entrada debe contener "
"polígonos."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5669
msgid ""
"The roundness of a polygon is defined as 4π × polygon area / perimeter². The"
" roundness value varies between 0 and 1. A perfect circle has a roundness of"
" 1, while a completely flat polygon has a roundness of 0."
msgstr ""
"La redondez de un polígono se define como 4π × área del polígono / "
"perímetro². El valor de la redondez varía entre 0 y 1. Un círculo perfecto "
"tiene una redondez de 1, mientras que un polígono completamente plano tiene "
"una redondez de 0."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5673
msgid "The algorithm returns NULL for multipart polygon features."
msgstr "El algoritmo devuelve NULL para entidades poligonales multiparte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5696
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5720
